<h3>Catalog Page</h3>

<p align="justify">A page with all products and their detailed descriptions. The page displays 6 products (the quantity is optional) in the left column. The right column displays the description of the first product. When the user scroll down to the 2nd product, the right column loads and displays the information about the second product. This happens till the user scrolls down to the last (6th) product, then they may load the next 6 products by pressing the 'Load  products' button (this is Infinity Scroll). </p>

